### Get all users
GET http://localhost:8080/users

### Get user by email
GET http://localhost:8080/users/email

### Get user's reports
GET http://localhost:8080/users/email/reports

### Update user
PATCH http://localhost:8080/users/email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "new-user1",
  "password": "asd"
}

### Delete user
DELETE http://localhost:8080/users/new-user1
